{"tid":722984,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"win10 laptop 聲音驅動經常出事","createTime":"2018-06-30T04:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T16:07:28.000Z","uid":117834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce7caedb4185684f422f6ec6037d7d92cced0b9","tid":722984,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"我就用緊DELL既XPS15 9575 2IN1 新買既 <br />\n<br />\n咁部機好多BUG就係人都知架啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我唔知關部機本身有問題定WIN10有問題<br />\n<br />\n成日部機CUM埋進入睡眠既時間開返<br />\n<br />\n部機好多時候都係無聲 但係禁入聲音設定果個位置係見到有聲輸出緊<br />\n<br />\n咁我通常都係重開機就無事或耆DISABLE左個REALTEK驅動再開返<br />\n<br />\n第二種情況就係睇睇下YOUTUBE可以無啦啦無左聲 仲要係畫面都播唔到好似死左FLASH咁<br />\n<br />\n咁我F5啦 播唔到又彈左句野出黎 SPOTIFY又係播唔到歌 顯示左句話我播唔到呢首歌之類<br />\n<br />\n咁我又係DISABLE左個聲音驅動或者重開機就無事<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟係DELL部機本身有問題定係WIN10 ?<br />\n<br />\n有咩解決方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c495e0e7e6b821244721ab620f504afc01ae0e3","tid":722984,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd952253a20fc76fa9173c6a585a7e7d3391e31","tid":722984,"uid":43823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"我都有呢個問題<br />\n無聲/細聲到聽唔到<br />\n一係就爆勁大沙沙聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （電視收唔到嗰d聲） <br />\n有裝ASIO,Ms surface laptop<br />\n打過去Ms問都係話重裝Realtek..."},{"pid":"87480c27a4de447bd25e35660f213ca77cbdbe6a","tid":722984,"uid":117834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cd952253a20fc76fa9173c6a585a7e7d3391e31","tid":722984,"uid":43823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s