al/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c020391adad46eff5d48caa71e71d8845dcea986","tid":722984,"uid":138658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"試下del咗個driver<br />\n上realtek裝返high definition audio driver<br />\n之前更新咗driver冇聲出 改做上面個driver就搞掂"}]}